en_148586_0	In order to further improve mental stability and attitudes and approaches of the troops, serving under the Security Force Headquarters – Jaffna (SFHQ-J), steps were taken to get the lecture assistance of Mrs Ama Dissanayake, a Consultant Psychotherapist and Counsellor.
en_148586_1	The workshop at the SFHQ-J auditorium on ‘Attitude Development and Mental Management’ headed by the Consultant took place on Sunday (12) with the participation of Officers and Other Ranks serving the Jaffna peninsula.
en_148586_2	Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya, Commander Security Forces - Jaffna has advised to organize the programme, attended by more than 300 Army personnel.
